main event: Multiple witnesses reported sightings of an unidentified flying object over Alto, Tennessee on April 7, 1966, describing it as metallic and bright.
interesting points: The UFO was observed by three different witnesses over a period of 2 hours and 30 minutes,The object was described as oval-shaped, dark on top and bright in the middle, and it made a high-frequency noise,The sightings occurred at different times and locations, with the object disappearing toward the south after 2.5 hours,Mr. Grover Morgan reported seeing a metallic object of about 25-30 feet in diameter hovering close to the ground, and multiple instances led to disturbances in nearby livestock during the sighting.
witness description: Civilians including Mr. John Doe and Mr. Grover Morgan
